        <mxCell id="4" parent="1" vertex="1" value="&lt;b&gt;How to read this slide&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;font color=#CC9900&gt;■ Gold frame&lt;/font&gt; = overlap (both swimlanes need these)&lt;br&gt;&lt;font color=#005AAB&gt;■ Blue box&lt;/font&gt; = shared GoF service we build &amp; operate&lt;br&gt;&lt;font color=#666666&gt;■ Grey column&lt;/font&gt; = mainly one swimlane today" style="text;html=1;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=left;fontSize=10">
