        <mxCell id="6" parent="1" vertex="1" value="• Adapter to MDO tools (not the math)&lt;br&gt;• Thousands of parallel design points&lt;br&gt;• Resilience when solvers fail mid-loop&lt;br&gt;• Uncertainty (UQ) ensembles" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#EEEEEE;strokeColor=#666666;align=left;verticalAlign=top;spacingLeft=10;spacingTop=8;fontSize=11;">
