        <mxCell id="8" parent="1" vertex="1" value="&lt;b&gt;OVERLAP — build once on GoF&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;font style='font-size:10px'&gt;Same platform service · both swimlanes · do not build twice&lt;/font&gt;" style="text;html=1;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=left;fontSize=10">
